name: Counts of Mysidacea sampled at night in Gazi Bay in October 1994
description: Counts of Mysidacea sp. (incl. sex and life stage) sampledat night in Gazi Bay and the West creek duringOctober 1994. 10 nightsamples were taken using a hyperbenthic sledge trawled by aboat at 25 HPfor 10 min (200m). The datawere digitized by VLIZ from the original report: Cattaert, S. (1997).Mysidacea van GaziBay, Kenya (staalnamecampagne Oktober 1994, nachtstalen); Mysidacea of Gazi Bay, Kenya (fieldwork campagne of 1994,night samples). Thesis. Universiteit Gent: Gent. 19 pp.
